snippet.title: An Empath’s Guide to Emotional vs. Physical Hunger with Amber Romaniuk
snippet.description:
Joined by emotional eating expert, Amber Romaniuk, Britt hosts a conversation that dives into understanding our emotional vs. physical hunger cues and the connection between emotional eating and those of us who are more sensitive. Plus be sure to checkout Amber’s Emotional Eating Quiz here: https://amberapproved.ca/emotional-eating-quiz/ 

  

  Enjoy and let us know your thoughts as we love hearing from this community!  

  

 Topics We Talk About: 

  Emotional eating The food industry  Food fear  Triggers of emotional eating Ways to overcome emotional eating Being an empath Diet culture  Eliminating food cravings    

 Find more at lovingyourownsoulpodcast.com 

  

 Resources: 

  Connect with Amber on Instagram: @amberromaniuk Gain body freedom for life: https://amberapproved.ca  No Sugarcoating Podcast: https://amberapproved.ca/podcast/  Emotional Eating Quiz: https://amberapproved.ca/emotional-eating-quiz/  Learn more about Britt’s holistic wellness coaching services and programs through Ambu at ambuwellness.com   Join my private Facebook Group:  A Modern Wellness Community  Learn more about Britt’s spiritual wellness retreat happening December 2021  Connect with me on Instagram @thebrittolson
